==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Betterment
<hw>Bet"ter*ment</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
making better; amendment; improvement.</def> <rj><au>W.
Montagu.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>An improvement of an estate which
renders it better than mere repairing would do; -- generally used in the
plural.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark> <rj><au>Bouvier.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bettermost</ent>⟦br⟧
